import React from 'react'
import { Box, TextField, Container, Typography, Button } from '@mui/material'

function Contact() {
    return (
        <Box sx={{ bgcolor: "silver", }}>
            <Container
                component="form"
                sx={{
                    '& .MuiTextField-root': { m: 1, width: '50ch' },

                    pb: 20,
                    pt: 10,
                    width: "50%", m: 'auto'
                }}
                noValidate
                autoComplete="off"
            >
                <Typography variant='h6'>Contact us :</Typography>
                <TextField
                    id="outlined-multiline-flexible"
                    label="Multiline"
                    multiline
                    rows={5}
                />
                <Button variant='contained' sx={{ml:2}}>Add Contact</Button>
            </Container>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default Contact
